      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 engine, renowned for its 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example utilizes a 6-speed manual transmission paired with a GKN-sourced variable M differential lock for superior mechanical traction. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, complemented by Electronic Damping Control (EDC) for optimized compression and rebound. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the high-pressure double-VANOS system operates with precision. A mechanically sound specimen for the purist seeking authentic atmospheric induction and hydraulic steering feedback.",
